snippet.title: Fire Emblem Engage — Fire Emblem For All — Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Whether you're new to the series or a battle-hardened veteran, Fire Emblem has something for everyone! From building out your ideal army to making friends along the way, Fire Emblem has something for everyone.
